<h2>My personas</h2>

<p>Personas define certain roles of your account. For instance you can have a persona for private 
use and another one for business context. When a relying party requests your information
you can choose the persona that you would like to exchange data from.</p>

<ul>
  <% @personas.each do |persona| %>
  <li>
		<h3><%=h persona.title%></h3>
		<div class="options">
			<%= link_to 'edit', edit_account_persona_url(persona) %>
			<%= link_to 'delete', account_persona_url(persona), :confirm => "Do you really want to delete the persona “#{h persona.title}”?", :method => :delete %>
		</div>
  </li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<%= link_to 'create a new persona', new_account_persona_url %>